From 5facc906d2b3e6696abdbd04ace99a4ec24e0633 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Fri, 27 Jun 2025 11:11:34 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 5/6] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: Move QCN9274 ring processing
 to dp_mon2.c

QCN9274 ring processing is currently part of ath12k/dp_mon.c
(ath12k.ko common module), with the Unified Driver framework,
QCN9274 adopts the monitor dual ring modle(mon2), so the ring
processing logic is being moved to the architecture-specific file
ath12k/wifi7/dp_mon2.c(ath12k_wifi7.ko arch specific module)

Patch-dependency:
	0404-0004-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Refactor-WCN7850-Destination.patch

Signed-off-by: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
